name: __EUpdateCompletionStatus
doc: Possible outcomes at the end of an update check

UpdateSuccess: Update completed successfully, some changes applied
UpdateSuccess_NoChange: Update completed successfully, no changed needed
UpdateSuccess_NeedsReload: Update completed successfully, need to reload the map
UpdateSuccess_NeedsRelaunch: Update completed successfully, need to relaunch the game
UpdateSuccess_NeedsPatch: Update completed successfully, a patch must be download to continue
UpdateFailure_PatchCheck: Update failed in the patch check
UpdateFailure_HotfixCheck: Update failed in the hotfix check
UpdateFailure_NotLoggedIn: Update failed due to not being logged in
